    android.widget.Adapter, android.widget.Filterable, android.widget.ListAdapter, android.widget.SpinnerAdapter, android.widget.ThemedSpinnerAdapter

    public class ListAdapterPicklist
extends android.widget.ArrayAdapter<PrimerTube>
    ListAdapterPicklist converts a list of PrimerTube objects into View items loaded into the ListView container.

    • Method Detail

      • checkBarcodeWithPrimer

        public void checkBarcodeWithPrimer(com.google.android.gms.vision.barcode.Barcode barcode)
        Checks for every PrimerTube object in the ListView if the barcode matches with a PrimerTube ID. If the values are the same, the fitting PrimerTube is taken from the storage.
        Parameters:
        barcode - the barcode that was scanned by the camera of the device

      • changeRow

        public void changeRow(PrimerTube newTube,
                      int positionForReplacement)
        Gets the data item associated with the specified position in the data set. The data of the item is changed, after a new PrimerTube has been requested.
        Parameters:
        newTube - the PrimerTube that replaces the old one. The replacement can be null, if there is no PrimerTube left.
        positionForReplacement - position of the PrimerTube in the ListView that is replaced.
